44
00:06:38,675 --> 00:06:40,875
Kurin<i>-chan</i>!

45
00:06:43,555 --> 00:06:45,245
Kurin<i>-chan...</i>

46
00:06:49,755 --> 00:06:51,915
Kurin<i>-chan</i>, where are you?

47
00:06:51,955 --> 00:06:54,525
Kurin<i>-chan</i>, where are you?!

48
00:06:54,565 --> 00:06:58,125
