<i>This all has to do with a</i>
<i>time when Goku was still a child.</i>

66
00:08:09,775 --> 00:08:15,265
<i>Goku had gone on a journey to both</i>
<i>train himself and search for the Dragon Balls.</i>

67
00:08:28,955 --> 00:08:29,955
<i>At that time,</i>

68
00:08:29,995 --> 00:08:33,655
<i>there was this terrible military outfit</i>
<i>calling themselves the Red Ribbon Army,</i>

69
00:08:33,695 --> 00:08:37,025
