70
00:08:37,065 --> 00:08:39,625
<i>Their boss, Commander Red,</i>

71
00:08:39,665 --> 00:08:44,435
<i>was gathering the Dragon Balls</i>
<i>to serve his evil purposes.</i>

72
00:08:44,475 --> 00:08:46,635
<i>Goku fought successively...</i>

73
00:08:46,675 --> 00:08:51,075
<i>...against a number of Red Ribbon</i>
<i>operatives who attacked him.</i>

74
00:08:55,715 --> 00:09:00,155
I took his face off!
Have I done something bad?

75
00:10:41,855 --> 00:10:48,285
<i>And then, Goku attacked the Red</i>
<i>Ribbon's headquarters all by himself!</i>

76
00:12:41,875 --> 00:12:44,735
<i>And that's how the Red</i>
<i>Ribbon Army was vanquished.</i>

77
00:12:44,775 --> 00:12:48,105
<i>At least, everyone thought they were vanquished.</i>

78
00:12:48,145 --> 00:12:51,915
<i>But there was someone who had survived.</i>

79
00:12:51,955 --> 00:12:54,845
<i>Doctor Gero, a maniacal scientist,</i>

80
00:12:54,885 --> 00:12:59,385
<i>secretly continued his research even</i>
<i>after the fall of the Red Ribbon Army.</i>

81
00:13:29,485 --> 00:13:33,055
<i>As such, he created these Artificial Humans,</i>

82
00:13:33,095 --> 00:13:36,255
<i>whose only desires were to kill and destroy,</i>

83
00:13:36,295 --> 00:13:39,055
<i>intending for them to be</i>
<i>the ultimate murder weapon.</i>

84
00:13:39,095 --> 00:13:43,295
<i>Those Artificial Humans are now running amuck.</i>

85
00:14:03,125 --> 00:14:06,285
So now Kuririn is assisting
Son Goku and his other friends...

86
00:14:06,325 --> 00:14:12,125
...in the fight against those
Artificial Humans on that southern island.

87
00:14:12,165 --> 00:14:14,135
