92
00:14:29,715 --> 00:14:33,085
I guess we really can't sense
any <i>ki</i> from the Artificial Humans.

93
00:14:49,735 --> 00:14:54,065
Incredible. Such strength!
So that's a Super Saiyan?

94
00:14:54,105 --> 00:14:57,545
It's a whole different dimension
from the rest of us. Far different.

95
00:14:58,675 --> 00:15:00,545
I'm not so sure...

96
00:15:46,125 --> 00:15:49,285
<i>His increase in power is much</i>
<i>greater than our data forecasted.</i>

97
00:15:49,325 --> 00:15:52,055
<i>This can't be happening.</i>

98
00:15:52,095 --> 00:15:56,695
<i>This isn't good! At this rate,</i>
<i>No. 1 9 will expend all of his energy...</i>

99
00:15:56,735 --> 00:15:58,505
